{"tid":1526053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣華視: 港鐵太子站濺血 港警車廂內無差別揮棍攻擊","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:34:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53199d095f068186e35ff3cfebe25fe78b0d9301","tid":1526053,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"香港反送中抗爭在昨(31)日晚間迎來最暴力混亂的情況，不但出現燃燒彈，警方還出動鎮暴水車。地鐵太子站還發生警民激烈衝突，大批警力衝入車廂內無差別揮棍攻擊，導致多名乘客頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中示威活動在31日晚間爆發史上最激烈的抗爭，有人在路中央焚燒路障，燃起熊熊大火，還有人投擲汽油彈，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至有民眾目睹「臥底警察」動用暴力挑起紛爭。警方也出動俗稱水砲車的鎮暴水車，場面相當混亂。就連地鐵車廂內都成為警民衝突的現場。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n車廂成戰場 胡椒噴霧.警棍毫不留情<br />\n<br />\n綜合香港媒體報導，有目擊民眾指出，起先是一般民眾和示威者在地鐵內發生爭執，突然有一名男子拿榔頭攻擊示威者，雙方爆發衝突，港鐵人員獲報後隨即停止載客，在太子站疏散所有乘客。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒想到此時速龍小組就衝進車廂內，無差別揮棍毆打，造成多人受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者指出，警方突然衝進太子站，在月台、地鐵車廂內掃蕩，見人就打，還在車廂內對下跪求饒的民眾近距離噴射胡椒噴霧。民眾企圖架起雨傘防禦，仍不敵警方的武力，多人被打到皮開肉綻，車廂內濺滿了鮮血。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港警方在今(1)日凌晨舉行記者會，宣稱香港經歷了「浩劫」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記者質疑警方在太子站內的無差別攻擊手段</strong></span>，警方強調，當下警員是憑藉著專業經驗，動用「適當武力」制伏示威者，共有40人被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/201909/201909011973239.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Finternational%2F201909%2F201909011973239.html&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=f8a5f654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/201909/201909011973239.html</a>"},{"pid":"d23df13db7da967eb20d98d0d9a79bc31d0ebfa9","tid":1526053,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=428898b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba443f26f52610b7b5f0467f9eba58aa78fccd61","tid":1526053,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beef2c94abaf9556157c5719ac33cc86191ee88e","tid":1526053,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"睇來刁帝想收台灣除咗出兵冇第2條路"},{"pid":"f64a859c741a88553361b5a59962c153636155ba","tid":1526053,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e22c78dd056b16ebb89db62f9ff1d179547c9e","tid":1526053,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a889a44998b8d16b02196c3702a7716e8e793b1f","tid":1526053,"uid":14305,"like":